data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of elegance, space, and functionality. As you step through door, you're greeted by a grand two-story foyer with charming chair window molding, setting the tone for the rest of the house. Archways and trey ceilings elevate its architectural charm, providing a sense of grandeur and sophistication that sets this home apart from the rest. The main level features a spacious living room with beautiful hardwood flooring, making it a cozy space for relaxation and entertainment. The family room, complete with a fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. This family room is open to the kitchen, making it an ideal setting for family gatherings and socializing. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, which boasts a central island, ample cabinet space, and a breakfast area. With a host of modern appliances, perfect for preparing delicious meals. The upper level offers a private retreat in the form of the master suite, accessible through double doors. Inside, you'll find a generously sized walk-in closet and a master bathroom with a double vanity, a relaxing soaking tub, and a separate shower. Three additional spacious bedrooms provide comfort and versatility for your family's needs. The convenient laundry room on the main floor simplifies daily chores. Step outside to the expansive backyard, featuring a patio area, providing the perfect space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property yours.
